d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好佩服小學老師嘅心機同耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對住初中我已經覺得佢地好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd9fa2c909778d91a85dabb645a5ccdd766ff32","tid":56473,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90cfffb05ac31864d42b3c00f49ffa78edf34b92","tid":56473,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73be686f5b739c3aec2ff0e75d06c99cca486d07","tid":56473,"uid":4863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教緊第一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知乜</blockquote><br />\n難唔難搵工？<br />\n巴打大學degree讀咩？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分享下教小一二三既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一年教，小二班主任，小一至四都有教下<br />\n越低班越難教，好似教BB咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一年就可以做班主任？會唔會handle唔到？"},{"pid":"20793111edeec13b6a96dc148963633bd1b1aa22","tid":56473,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c734ef56136dd369118b6c1e8ba0dfa799a11340","tid":56473,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教緊第一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知乜</blockquote><br />\n難唔難搵工？<br />\n巴打大學degree讀咩？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分享下教小一二三既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一年教，小二班主任，小一至四都有教下<br />\n越低班越難教，好似教BB咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教咩科？係咩degree讀咩無所謂架<br />\n<br />\n巴打做得開唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁細個點樣上堂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教英文、常，要搭術科教，我音體視都唔識，就教下電腦<br />\n教得開心既，係岀卷呀、搞學校野好煩<br />\n同學生講每樣野都要好清楚，咁細個要好有耐性，預左要講多幾次<br />\n小學咩degree都無所謂既，讀左PGDE就OK&hellip;不過語文科要專科專教，入左行之後要補番個相關既master&hellip;巴打想教乜？<br />\n利申：我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專科專教係咩？<br />\n其實我唔想教太細個  <br />\n想教中學多啲 小學想教啲高年級<br />\n但邊輪到我揀<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家讀緊個degree 都無機會教中學<br />\n睇下自己有無機會教小學<br />\n咩科就真係無所謂 小學野都handle到<br />\n係怕唔識教太細個"},{"pid":"1bf0970063a0155830f0ad7a98228252d0b85f85","tid":56473,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n難唔難搵工？<br />\n巴打大學degree讀咩？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分享下教小一二三既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一年教，小二班主任，小一至四都有教下<br />\n越低班越難教，好似教BB咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教咩科？係咩degree讀咩無所謂架<br />\n<br />\n巴打做得開唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁細個點樣上堂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好佩服小學老師嘅心機同耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對住初中我已經覺得佢地好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打都係做緊老師?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得小五小六都ok呀<br />\n係低B左少少 但起碼係知自己講緊咩做緊咩<br />\n都溝通到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9affd43cec9179d5b58f1478057aa18862a0dedc","tid":56473,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"想知道 23歲值唔值得用幾年時間同金錢讀完source再做小教<br />\n呢個問題諗左我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好鐘意同小朋友嘻嘻哈哈教下書傾下計<br />\n但係唔知讀完幾年出到黎會唔會唔係我諗既咁"},{"pid":"407aee3462293af2f3837b2f0068a066134c3c0e","tid":56473,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知道 23歲值唔值得用幾年時間同金錢讀完source再做小教<br />\n呢個問題諗左我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好鐘意同小朋友嘻嘻哈哈教下書傾下計<br />\n但係唔知讀完幾年出到黎會唔會唔係我諗既咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀完 嗰啲教育課程"},{"pid":"34be8ed09ef12299857ac93212d73c8623a771fb","tid":56473,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"推出天際"},{"pid":"a2d2772a387b3212cd25d58ae714e1d61c74033a","tid":56473,"uid":55084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知道 23歲值唔值得用幾年時間同金錢讀完source再做小教<br />\n呢個問題諗左我好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好鐘意同小朋友嘻嘻哈哈教下書傾下計<br />\n但係唔知讀完幾年出到黎會唔會唔係我諗既咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你讀個英文pgde就唔會失業嫁啦"},{"pid":"54c26eb1da80f120b32c65f4669d2891a973f2e6","tid":56473,"uid":32359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n第一年教，小二班主任，小一至四都有教下<br />\n越低班越難教，好似教BB咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教咩科？係咩degree讀咩無所謂架<br />\n<br />\n巴打做得開唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁細個點樣上堂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教英文、常，要搭術科教，我音體視都唔識，就教下電腦<br />\n教得開心既，係岀卷呀、搞學校野好煩<br />\n同學生講每樣野都要好清楚，咁細個要好有耐性，預左要講多幾次<br />\n小學咩degree都無所謂既，讀左PGDE就OK&hellip;不過語文科要專科專教，入左行之後要補番個相關既master&hellip;巴打想教乜？<br />\n利申：我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問重唔重視dse成績同邊間出身？讀教大易唔易搵到小學教席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該絲打"},{"pid":"142a11c24efca271b610c847f6d5385cea9508bc","tid":56473,"uid":67917,"l